{"tid":379941,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"Hairspray可以Hand Carry?","createTime":"2017-08-29T17:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T03:26:22.000Z","uid":75118,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a76f03ad6b4636f304fb71c7f759cd40465c50a","tid":379941,"uid":75118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:41:22.000Z","msg":"一直以黎都係聽人講話Hairspray唔比拎上機,<br />\n即使寄倉都要鬼鬼鼠鼠。<br />\n但我望一望國泰個網 (<a href=\"https://www.cathaypacific.com/cx/zh_HK/travel-information/baggage/controlled-and-banned-items/liquids-aerosols-and-gels.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cathaypacific.com%2Fcx%2Fzh_HK%2Ftravel-information%2Fbaggage%2Fcontrolled-and-banned-items%2Fliquids-aerosols-and-gels.html&d=pjaYt0RjaqmNpsRvj%2FdAAf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=a914c68e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cathaypacific.com/cx/zh_HK/travel-information/baggage/controlled-and-banned-items/liquids-aerosols-and-gels.html</a>),<br />\n好似寫住<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">您可攜帶液體、壓縮氣體及凝膠狀物體登機</span>，惟每名旅客只可攜帶的物品的每項總容量不得超過 100 毫升並載於一個容量不超過 1 公升的可再封口透明膠袋內」</blockquote><br />\n然後佢example果度都寫住<br />\n<blockquote>物品類別<br />\n請使用以下液體、凝膠狀物體或壓縮氣體類別作為指引：<br />\n<br />\n凝膠狀物體，如髮膠或沐浴露<br />\n乳霜及液體，如太陽油或香體露<br />\n膏狀物體，如牙膏或凡士林（只限與嬰兒同行）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">壓縮泡沫及噴霧，如剃鬚泡沫或壓縮香體露<br />\n</span>食品，如水或乳酪<br />\n液體化妝品，如粉底或脣彩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">所以想問下, 如果Hairspray係100ml以下, 係唔係都可以Hand carry拎上機?</span></ins></strong>"},{"pid":"57e8f872c2bc25f59fd6d12880746fb883bf3071","tid":379941,"uid":8528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:49:50.000Z","msg":"寄倉"},{"pid":"ec3c847fe712e030f5c16b08c5fa6f308eb4c970","tid":379941,"uid":75118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:52:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寄倉</blockquote><br />\n即係佢個網寫錯定點?<br />\n<br />\n因為佢個網係寫住<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n您可攜帶液體、壓縮氣體及凝膠狀物體登機，惟每名旅客只可攜帶的物品的每項總容量不得超過 100 毫升並載於一個容量不超過 1 公升的可再封口透明膠袋內。詳情請參閱下文。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">超過此上限的物品應放於寄艙行李內</span>。請注意：機場保安人員將於您起飛前沒收不符合有關要求的物品。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n我唔係應該assume佢呢篇野係for hand carry咩?"},{"pid":"2d9159cece535ffa59fd054e8c64e6c57c2a6629","tid":379941,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:56:15.000Z","msg":"直接寄唔洗煩啦<br />\n你上機要gel頭定點"},{"pid":"0e5727f8ef2ea15031dffa0e2d176fac49a082e7","tid":379941,"uid":61712,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T18:00:33.000Z","msg":"一定要寄 唔寄就扔你 你諗你要唔要冒險啦 不過一定係比人扔"},{"pid":"79a3c7710ca0b0f723762870f412da7783f0d6dc","tid":379941,"uid":75118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T01:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直接寄唔洗煩啦<br />\n你上機要gel頭定點</blockquote><br />\n因為唔諗住寄任何行李"},{"pid":"8b1643ebc1796e7e6787d3293ddfc8209f334765","tid":379941,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T01:15:40.000Z","msg":"寄倉都會先叫你開喼check"},{"pid":"0451ea250ca7f328550a25bbf9e9cf6ef0287e51","tid":379941,"uid":59929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T01:16:42.000Z","msg":"應該係以機場安檢為標準<br />\n全世界機場標準唔同"},{"pid":"cb1833b9bf644770d0a7071c9e4e74a4614d928a","tid":379941,"uid":82903,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T01:19:28.000Z","msg":"100ml 以下可以hand carry, <br />\n用透明袋裝住，過x光個陣畀佢check"},{"pid":"baf56c58a74bde3e12154bbfb7e2a524cb27e354","tid":379941,"uid":82718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T07:38:28.000Z","msg":"可以Hand Carry"},{"pid":"2ab800e7ae83667a4463ad72bbcd3b357bbd8552","tid":379941,"uid":75118,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:43:40.000Z","msg":"唔明班人負評d乜，<br />\n剩係見呢個post度有人話得，有人話唔得，<br />\n就知呢個問題根本好多人都唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161b24f815aaf1a2830be76a18a812ddaae7ff66","tid":379941,"uid":90166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor